Salesforce Queue Refresher

This Chrome Extension automatically refreshes Case Queues within Salesforce Classic every 30 seconds without reloading the page.

The script starts automatically, no need to toggle anything after install.

---

Installation

1) Extract the archive to a folder where you would like the extension to be stored on your computer.

2) Open Google Chrome

3) Navigate to chrome://extensions

4) Toggle "Developer mode"

5) Click 'Load unpacked'

6) Select the folder you created in step 1

7) Visit a queue in Salesforce Classic and watch it refresh every 30 seconds until the end of time

